  <pharmacodynamics>Extracts of _Sarracenia purpurea_ may enhance glucose uptake by attenuating glucose-6-phosphatase enzymatic activity and decreasing hepatic glucose production [A32510]. In an in vitro model of glucotoxicity in PC12 cells, treatment of _Sarracenia purpurea_ demonstrated cytoprotective effects and prevented glucose-mediated cell loss [A32509].</pharmacodynamics>
  <mechanism-of-action>The full mechanism of action of the antidiabetic and cytoprotective activity is not fully elucidated. </mechanism-of-action>
